usive-green-band-trailer-taking-deborah-logan|title=Exclusive Green Band Trailer for The Taking of Deborah Logan|date=September 22, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[X-Men: Apocalypse]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes|Story}}\n| {{yes|Cameo}}\n| As security guard\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Bohemian Rhapsody (film)|Bohemian Rhapsody]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n| \n| \n| Directed and produced (uncredited) film during development, pre-production and majority of production\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Dark Phoenix (film)|Dark Phoenix]]''\n| \n| {{yes}}\n| \n| \n| Uncredited producer during development and pre-production. Removed from production and credits amidst sexual assault allegations{{dubious|date=January 2020}}\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! rowspan=2 | Year\n! rowspan=2 | Title\n! colspan=4 | Credited as\n! rowspan=2 class=\"unsortable\" |Notes\n|-\n! width=65 |director\n! width=65 |[[Film producer|Producer]]\n! width=65 |screenWriter\n! width=65 |Actor\n|-\n| 2004\u20132012\n| ''[[House (TV series)|House]]''\n| {{yes}} (2004)\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n|\n| {{yes}}\n| Episodes: \"[[Pilot (House)|Pilot]]\" (also known as \"Everybody Lies\"), \"[[Occam's Razor (House)|Occam's Razor]]\" and \"[[Sports Medicine (House)|Sports Medicine]]\"\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[The Triangle (miniseries)|The Triangle]]''\n|\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|\n| [[Miniseries]]\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''The Science of Superman''\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n|\n| [[Television documentary|TV documentary]]\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Football Wives]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes}}\n|\n|\n| Episode: \"Pilot\"\n|-\n| 2007\u20132009\n| ''[[Dirty Sexy Money]]''\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''Valkyrie: The Plot to Kill Hitler''\n|\n| {{yes}}\n|\n|\n| [[Television documentary|TV documentary]]\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Mockingbird Lane]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n|\n|\n| TV special\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Battle Creek (TV series)|Battle Creek]]''\n| {{yes}}\n| {{yes|Executive}}\n|\n|\n| Episode: \"The Battle Creek Way\"\n|-\n| 20